{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e29fd8288a","title":"“章伯钧不是反革命”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"511016a59a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"e29fd8288a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"06dd5d9eb9","name":"北京地质勘探学院师生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ce67e4d369","type":"title","text":"“章伯钧不是反革命”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e29fd8288a"},{"id":"55e6854e5a","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院师生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e29fd8288a"},{"id":"464ec6e521","type":"paragraph","text":"××说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e29fd8288a"},{"id":"f4e169a205","type":"paragraph","text":"「章伯钧承认中华人民共和国宪法，……只是和党共分天下，章伯钧反党要政权，并不是以武器来夺取……」","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e29fd8288a"},{"id":"dd83d8e107","type":"paragraph","text":"「我看他要平分天下，并不要全部政权，要两党轮流执政，……这不是反革命。」","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e29fd8288a"},{"id":"efaa20b4b8","type":"paragraph","text":"××说：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e29fd8288a"},{"id":"d56ce3edd0","type":"paragraph","text":"「章伯钧的两院制的说法，看不出有反党的地方，只是有一些地方讲得不正确，给一县由民主党派来领导，看结果如何？」","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e29fd8288a"},{"id":"b9b9363da1","type":"paragraph","text":"××说：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e29fd8288a"},{"id":"82db77e7a0","type":"paragraph","text":"「无产阶级专政就是共产党专政，因为a＝b，b＝c，所以a＝c。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e29fd8288a"},{"id":"e8b5b556ec","type":"paragraph","text":"「三害的根源好象是民主专制制度产生的，过去没有，现在才听见，过去就没有人讲过三害。」","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e29fd8288a"}],"page":{"id":"dee17186d6","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articl